&gt;&gt; It's fancy, all right.

00:00:29.140 --> 00:00:30.020
&gt;&gt; Okay.

00:00:30.020 --> 00:00:32.314
&gt;&gt; Seriously,
Firebase is a collection of services,

00:00:32.314 --> 00:00:35.825
including a database that can serve
as a simple backend for your app.

00:00:35.825 --> 00:00:38.605
&gt;&gt; Okay, that sounds great, but
is it easy to use with Android?

00:00:38.605 --> 00:00:39.145
&gt;&gt; Very easy.

00:00:39.145 --> 00:00:42.785
