set up an account, so you and

00:01:02.820 --> 00:01:04.840
your developer can poke
around with the SDK.

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:06.250
&gt;&gt; All right, that sound great!

00:01:06.250 --> 00:01:07.990
&gt;&gt; Follow me, and
let's get started with Firebase.

